00:02:16.573 --> 00:02:24.386
It's got 115 bhp and with this version, the 208 Allure,
costs 21.250 Euros.

00:02:24.387 --> 00:02:29.268
But pricing of the 208 starts at around 13.000 Euros.

00:02:29.269 --> 00:02:32.974
That is a gasoline car with a 1.0 engine, which is a new engine.

00:02:32.975 --> 00:02:39.484
This is a multigrain, tree hugging, environmental engine.

00:02:47.888 --> 00:02:50.988
Peugeot also put some effort into
upgrading the interior.

00:02:50.989 --> 00:02:55.046
On terms of design they achieved this.

00:02:55.047 --> 00:02:57.741
But the usage and combinations of materials isn't quite ideal.

00:02:57.742 --> 00:03:01.096
It's got a leather steering wheel, quite nice.

00:03:02.132 --> 00:03:05.377
But together with this there's cheap plastic over here.

00:03:07.508 --> 00:03:10.352
There's elves living there or something like that.

00:03:10.353 --> 00:03:14.465
It looks ridiculous.

00:03:18.714 --> 00:03:20.577
Should you buy a 208?

00:03:21.336 --> 00:03:22.523
I think it's kind of fun.

00:03:22.524 --> 00:03:29.363
Peugeot's been very busy making the car more fun to drive 
by reducing the weight and what not.

00:03:30.135 --> 00:03:36.752
But an ordinary diesel isn't exciting so let's hope the 155 bhp
gasoline version is more fun.

00:03:37.218 --> 00:03:40.340
Maybe a 208 GTI will be released, that would
be so much fun.

00:03:40.341 --> 00:03:45.515
A 208 GTI, a light steering paradise,
how lovely.

00:03:46.991 --> 00:03:50.370
