00:04:30.849 --> 00:04:37.310
If you need to pick a lease-car of a small second car,
than this car is a good option.

00:04:37.311 --> 00:04:41.529
It gives you a lot of fun for a few bucks.

00:04:45.995 --> 00:04:48.854
This is going to be the ultimate rental.

00:04:48.855 --> 00:04:54.616
When you pick up this car at your rental you
might find it boring at first.

00:04:54.617 --> 00:04:56.937
But this will change into fun when
you drive it.

00:04:56.938 --> 00:05:00.600
A fun car, good steering, nice sounds,
just great.

